OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772565072
OL,3,C'Stupid and childish' man drove 18-
OL,4,Ctonne coach into ex's bedroom window
OL,6,FA coach company employee who drove an
OL,7,F18-tonne single-decker into his ex-
OL,8,Fpartner's home has been told by a
OL,9,Fjudge it was a "ludicrous,
OL,10,Firresponsible, stupid and childish"
OL,11,Fthing to do.
OL,13,FIan Anderson, 33, drove the coach into
OL,14,Fthe bedroom window of the address in
OL,15,FAshington, Northumberland, on 21
OL,16,FJanuary last year, while his ex was
OL,17,Finside.
OL,26,@qD@POUrD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
