FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772565072
OL,3,C'Stupid and childish' man drove 18-
OL,4,Ctonne coach into ex's bedroom window
OL,6,FNewcastle Crown Court heard that the
OL,7,Fimpact caused #23,834 of damage to the
OL,8,Fground floor flat and #22,000 of
OL,9,Fdamage to the vehicle, which belonged
OL,10,Fto Liberty Coaches, where Anderson
OL,11,Fworked as a yard man.
OL,13,FMr Anderson, of Boldon, South
OL,14,FTyneside, previously admitted
OL,15,Faggravated vehicle taking, causing
OL,16,Fcriminal damage to the property and
OL,17,Fdangerous driving.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772565072
OL,3,C'Stupid and childish' man drove 18-
OL,4,Ctonne coach into ex's bedroom window
OL,6,FRecorder Tony Hedworth KC handed him a
OL,7,F12-month jail sentence, suspended for
OL,8,Ftwo years, a two-year driving ban and
OL,9,Fordered him to pay #1,000 compensation
OL,10,Fto the housing company and the coach
OL,11,Ffirm to cover their insurance excesses.
OL,13,FThe court heard that Anderson and his
OL,14,Fpartner of seven years had split up
OL,15,Fthe month before the incident.
OL,17,FAnderson took a coach from his
OL,18,Femployer's yard in Cramlington and
OL,19,Fdrove to his ex's, where he beeped the
OL,20,Fhorn outside.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772565072
OL,3,C'Stupid and childish' man drove 18-
OL,4,Ctonne coach into ex's bedroom window
OL,6,FHis former boyfriend was in his
OL,7,Fbedroom at the time and he noticed the
OL,8,Fwhite coach before it was driven at
OL,9,Fthe building.
OL,11,FIt was driven into a wall, causing
OL,12,Ffour windows to smash, a radiator to
OL,13,Fcome off the wall and structural
OL,14,Fdamage.
OL,16,FAnderson then shouted "get outside" to
OL,17,Fhis ex, who remained inside the
OL,18,Fproperty, the court heard.
OL,26,@xD@WOUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
