OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772565072
OL,3,C'Stupid and childish' man drove 18-
OL,4,Ctonne coach into ex's bedroom window
OL,6,FRecorder Hedworth told Anderson: "You
OL,7,Fcan make a scene with your ex-partner,
OL,8,Fyou can try to embarrass them but you
OL,9,Fdon't do it with someone else's very
OL,10,Fexpensive property and you don't do it
OL,11,Fwith someone else's home, provided by
OL,12,Fa social housing group.
OL,14,F"This was a ludicrously irresponsible,
OL,15,Fstupid and childish thing to do.
OL,17,F"You weren't doing it with toys, you
OL,18,Fwere doing it with very expensive
OL,19,Fproperty."
OL,26,@nD@bOUvD@AOUyD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
