OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772565072
OL,3,C'Stupid and childish' man drove 18-
OL,4,Ctonne coach into ex's bedroom window
OL,6,FThe judge imposed a restraining order
OL,7,Fpreventing Anderson from entering
OL,8,Fparts of Ashington.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/7
